{
  "stem": "2684.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And back in the same-- I don't know whether the same block, but the similar block when I was in the first time in December.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was in a different condition.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was completely gone as far as human concern.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were there for about one or two days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we already heard-- hearing the gunshots very close, and we knew that the-- the freedom, whatever that means-- meant that time is not very far.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you come to a mental stage where you do not comprehend practically nothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Your state of body is unimportant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Your mind is unimportant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Your-- your-- your existence is unimportant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Is nothing is important.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It just-- it's like a blur.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know you are living, but you're not thinking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You are a zombie-- a muselman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And about two days, three days later, suddenly the doors open and the Russian [GERMAN], or what we call the caretakers, comes in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And with a broken English he said, and-- no German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He said, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And as it didn't meant anything to you, it didn't meant anything to me either.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I knew the war was over, but-- and I didn't realize until I come out from the hospital that I had a typhus, the fleck typhus, which affected everybody who had.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the guy said [GERMAN], and that meant the war is over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The war is over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And about 15 minutes later, the door opens death slowly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I had only energy to look.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And came in an American soldier-- later on we knew he's American-- with the hat and the net, and the net is full of greens, and all the camouflage, what a front soldier wears.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
